- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is also likely as the paper discusses a distributed volunteer-based approach for running evolutionary algorithm experiments. 
- cs.Distributed is another possible category as the paper focuses on distributed computing. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper discusses the implementation of a JavaScript framework for evolutionary algorithms. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also a possible category as the paper presents an application for running distributed volunteer-based evolutionary algorithm experiments.
